# Cross-repo siblings the dev-shell CI jobs (lint, test) clone adjacent to this
# checkout so config.nims's sibling detection can resolve them. The shared
# `clone-siblings` action (run by setup-dev-env) reads this file.
#
# `name=ref` clones the ref directly; plain `name` resolves the revision from
# the per-commit workspace lock in metacraft-manifests. reprobuild is not yet
# integrated into the lock contract, so pin the mainline branch explicitly.
#
# These carry codetracer's canonical incremental test engine
# (src/ct_test/incremental) and the trace-format-nim CTFS reader it imports,
# reached through ct_incremental_adapter (the engine-free seam). One-way
# dependency: reprobuild -> codetracer.
codetracer=dev
codetracer-trace-format-nim=dev
